1955;;The Lyons in Paris;;British;;Val Guest;;Ben Lyon, Bebe Daniels;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Lyons_in_Paris;;Has Ben Lyon forgotten his wedding anniversary? His wife Bebe thinks he has, and can hardly contain her fury. When his son Richard sees him dining with a glamorous French singer he thinks the worst. But Ben is actually buying tickets from her, and he surprises everyone with a family holiday to Paris. Once in Paris, there are further misunderstandings involving the singer, trouble with an antique car, as well as visits to a seedy nightclub and to the famous Folies Berg√®re.